High Availability Authorization Server

Never deploy a single Authorization Server.

Instead:

Load Balancer
                    │
      ┌─────────────┼──────────────┐
      ▼             ▼              ▼
 Authorization   Authorization   Authorization
 Server A        Server B        Server C

If one dies,

another immediately serves the request.

This is standard HA deployment.


